## Extensions Quick Reference

| Extension | Enable SQL | Best for |
|---|---|---|
| `vector` | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS vector` | AI/semantic search, embeddings |
| `pg_cron` | Already enabled | Scheduled jobs, cleanup, sync |
| `pg_net` | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pg_net` | HTTP from triggers, webhooks |
| `pgmq` | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pgmq` | Background job queues |
| `pg_stat_statements` | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pg_stat_statements` | Slow query analysis |
| `index_advisor` | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS index_advisor` | Missing index suggestions |
| `hypopg` | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS hypopg` | Test indexes safely |
| `pg_jsonschema` | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pg_jsonschema` | Validate JSONB structure |
| `PostGIS` | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS postgis` | Geospatial/location queries |
